                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Providence</placeName>\n                <date>Sunday</date> Morning</p>\n            <p><date>November 30, 1859</date>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Mr Editor</p>\n            <p>Knowing that you are interested<lb/> in the welfare of the <sic>hebrew</sic>\n                congregations through<lb/>out the <placeName>United States</placeName>, and\n                    <sic>allways</sic><lb/> ready, to insert in your valuable<lb/> Paper all facts\n                concerning our<lb/> holy Religion, I take pleasure<lb/> of informing you of the following<lb/>\n                <del>facts</del> About two years ago <persName>Mr<lb/> A. Wormser</persName>\n                <sic>than</sic> a resident of<lb/> this city, has at that time remo<lb/>ved with his\n                family to <placeName>New York</placeName>,<lb/> and from that city left for\n                        <placeName>Uropa<add>?</add></placeName><lb/> to <del>get</del> see those\n                that where dear<lb/> to him, and on saying good <sic>by</sic><lb/> to his Brethren\n                of the congregation<lb/> San<add>?</add> of Israel <sic>hi</sic> promised, if<lb/>\n                his life was spared to return in<lb/>\n                <sic>safty</sic> to this country, <sic>hi</sic> would</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3dz03n42/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
