                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>List, and that his Name may be<lb/> mentioned at each prayer the<lb/> meeting\n                    <sic>than</sic> adjourned, and<lb/> the President invited the Ladies<lb/> and\n                Gentlemen to the honor<lb/> of <persName>Mr Joseph Stern</persName> to a<lb/> repast\n                prepared for this ocas<lb/>sion, ample justice was done<lb/> to all eatables, and\n                the company<lb/> brook<add>?</add> up much pleased.</p>\n            <p>Mr Editor</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">You please insert the<lb/> above as an editorial and<lb/> send your\n                Bill for payment.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\"><persName role=\"author\">A Goldsmith</persName> Sec.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Per B D</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
